'''彭迪思'''<ref name="星島160614">{{Cite news | url=http://calgary.singtao.ca/311150/2016-06-14/post-%E5%89%8D%E7%9C%81%E9%95%B7%E5%BD%AD%E8%BF%AA%E6%80%9D-%E4%BB%BB%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%81%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F/?variant=zh-hk | title=前省長彭迪思 任美企能源顧問 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2016-06-14 | accessdate=2016-10-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018204512/http://calgary.singtao.ca/311150/2016-06-14/post-%E5%89%8D%E7%9C%81%E9%95%B7%E5%BD%AD%E8%BF%AA%E6%80%9D-%E4%BB%BB%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%81%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F/?variant=zh-hk | archive-date=2016-10-18 | dead-url=yes }}</ref> {{post-nominals|country=CAN|PC|QC}}（{{lang|en|Peter Eric James "Jim" Prentice}}，{{bd|1956年|7月20日|catIdx=M|2016年|10月13日}}<ref name="CBC161013">{{Cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/jim-prentice-plane-crash-killed-1.3804941 | title=Former Alberta premier Jim Prentice among 4 killed in B.C. plane crash | date=2016-10-13 | accessdate=2016-10-14 | publisher=CBC News | archive-date=2018-04-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180428011411/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/jim-prentice-plane-crash-killed-1.3804941 | dead-url=no }}</ref>），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物，2014年至2015年間擔任第16任[[亞伯達省省長|亞伯達省省長]]<ref>[http://calgary.ctvnews.ca/jim-prentice-officially-sworn-in-as-alberta-s-premier-1.2007122] {{Wayback|url=http://calgary.ctvnews.ca/jim-prentice-officially-sworn-in-as-alberta-s-premier-1.2007122 |date=20201111213353 }} - Jim Prentice Officially Sworn In as Alberta's Premier -  retrieved 15 September 2014</ref>、亞伯達進步保守黨黨魁<ref>{{cite news|title=Alberta PC leadership vote: Jim Prentice wins on 1st ballot|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/alberta-pc-leadership-vote-jim-prentice-wins-on-1st-ballot-1.2758180|accessdate=September 6, 2014|work=CBC News|date=September 6, 2014|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513032950/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/alberta-pc-leadership-vote-jim-prentice-wins-on-1st-ballot-1.2758180|dead-url=no}}</ref>及[[亞伯達省議會|亞伯達省議會]]卡加利-山麓選區省議員。在此之前他則從2004年至2010年間出任[[加拿大國會下議院|加拿大國會下議院]]卡加利中北選區議員，期間曾在[[加拿大保守黨|加拿大保守黨]]執政期間擔任工業部長和環境部長等[[加拿大内閣|聯邦内閣]]職位。他於2016年遇上空難逝世，終年60歲<ref name=CBC161013/><ref name="Global161014"/>。

==早年生活==
彭迪思生於[[安大略省|安大略省]]北部的南波庫派恩鎮（{{lang|en|South Porcupine}}），在家中排行第三，有兩名姊姊和兩名妹妹<ref name="ABAssembly">{{cite web |title=The Honourable Jim Prentice, PC, QC, 2014-2015 |url=https://www.assembly.ab.ca/lao/library/premiers/j-prentice.html |accessdate=2016-10-19 |work=亞伯達省議會 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422141919/https://www.assembly.ab.ca/lao/library/premiers/j-prentice.html }}</ref>。父親艾里克（{{lang|en|Eric Prentice}}）為一金礦工人並曾任職業冰球員，主要效力小型聯賽的隊伍但亦曾於1943年-44年賽季五度為[[國家冰球聯盟|國家冰球聯盟]]的[[多倫多楓葉隊|多倫多楓葉隊]]上陣<ref name=CBC161013/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ourontario.ca/timmins/2441681/data |title=Mawhinney, Wilma Lyle Marea  and  Prentice, Eric Dayton ,  (Married) |publisher= |access-date=2016-10-15 |archive-date=2019-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519180127/http://news.ourontario.ca/timmins/2441681/data }}</ref>。1969年，艾里克改到[[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]]的煤礦工作，彭迪思舉家遷至當地。彭迪思年少時亦熱衷冰球，但因一次賽事膝部受傷而未能繼續體育生涯，並在父親鼓勵下決定成為律師<ref name="Torstar161014">{{Cite news | url=https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2016/10/14/timeline-of-the-career-of-the-late-jim-prentice.html | title=Timeline of the career of the late Jim Prentice | author=Edwards, Peter | publisher=《多倫多星報》 | date=2016-10-14 | accessdate=2016-10-15 | archive-date=2020-11-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107125827/https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2016/10/14/timeline-of-the-career-of-the-late-jim-prentice.html }}</ref>。他於1977年從[[亞伯達大學|亞伯達大學]]取得商科學士學位後到[[達爾豪西大學|達爾豪西大學]]攻讀法律，1980年畢業，當中數年夏季在煤礦當暑期工以幫補學費<ref>[http://www.ic.gc.ca/epic/site/ic1.nsf/en/01530e.html Speaking Points - The Honourable Jim Prentice - Canadian Council of Chief Executives Luncheon, Toronto, Ontario, November 21, 2007] - Industry Canada - retrieved 11 June 2008</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Former Alberta premier saw public life as a 'noble calling'|url=https://www.ualberta.ca/news-and-events/newsarticles/2016/october/former-alberta-premier-saw-public-life-as-a-noble-calling|accessdate=2016-10-15|work=[[亞伯達大學|亞伯達大學]]|date=2016-10-14|author=Betkowski, Bet|coauthor=Brown, Mike|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161015010107/https://www.ualberta.ca/news-and-events/newsarticles/2016/october/former-alberta-premier-saw-public-life-as-a-noble-calling|archive-date=2016-10-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Prentice under pressure|url=https://alumni.dal.ca/news/alumni/prentice-under-pressure/|accessdate=2016-10-15|work=[[達爾豪西大學|達爾豪西大學]]|date=2014-04-24|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520212540/https://alumni.dal.ca/news/alumni/prentice-under-pressure/}}</ref>。

彭迪思獲得律師資格後與夥伴在[[卡加利|卡加利]]成立律師事務所，專注土地權益事務，並於1992年獲得[[御用大律師|御用大律師]]資格<ref>{{cite web|title=Premier Jim Prentice memorial|url=http://www.alberta.ca/jim-prentice-memorial.cfm|accessdate=2016-10-15|work=亞伯達省政府|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014231647/http://www.alberta.ca/jim-prentice-memorial.cfm|archivedate=2016-10-14}}</ref>。他於1983年與同為律師的卡倫·齊格勒（{{lang|en|Karen Ziegler}}）結婚，兩人育有三名女兒<ref name="ABAssembly"/>。

==涉足政治==
彭迪思於1976年加入[[加拿大進步保守黨|加拿大進步保守黨]]，並參與[[喬·克拉克|-{zh-hans:乔·克拉克;zh-hk:祖·卡勒;zh-tw:喬·克拉克;}-]]同年角逐該黨黨魁的助選工作，又於1985年協助蓋蒂（{{lang|en|Don Getty}}）角逐亞伯達進步保守黨黨魁<ref name="Torstar161014"/>。他於1986年亞伯達省選首次參選，代表亞省進步保守黨角逐卡加利山景選區省議員席位，但不敵省新民主黨候選人<ref>{{cite news|title=A 1986 photo of Jim Prentice|url=http://www.ottawacitizen.com/news/1986+photo+Prentice+Prentice+Progressive+Conservative+candidate+Calgary+Mountain+View+defeated+candidate+Hawkesworth+Prentice+wife+Karen+stare+glumly+election+results+Photo+Calgary+Herald+file+photo+originally+published+1986/10182250/story.html|accessdate=19 February 2016|work=Ottawa Citizen|publisher=Postmedia|date=September 6, 2014|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520101237/http://www.ottawacitizen.com/news/1986+photo+Prentice+Prentice+Progressive+Conservative+candidate+Calgary+Mountain+View+defeated+candidate+Hawkesworth+Prentice+wife+Karen+stare+glumly+election+results+Photo+Calgary+Herald+file+photo+originally+published+1986/10182250/story.html}}</ref>。他在往後年間為聯邦進步保守黨從事幕後工作，包括從1991年-94年擔任該黨的司庫<ref name="Torstar161014"/>。

2002年，彭迪思贏取聯邦進步保守黨的候選人提名，代表該黨角逐[[加拿大國會下議院|加拿大國會下議院]]的卡加利西南選區議席補選。另一方面，[[加拿大聯盟|加拿大聯盟]]的新任黨魁[[斯蒂芬·哈珀|哈珀]]則尚未持有國會議席，因此未能在議事廳内代表該黨。加拿大政黨素有慣例，在此情況下讓該名黨魁在無競爭對手的情況下贏取議席，彭迪思因此退選<ref>{{cite book|last1=Plamondon|first1=Bob|title=Full Circle: Death and Resurrection In Canadian Conservative Politics|date=Nov 21, 2014|publisher=eBookIt.com|pages=370-375|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=eZyMBQAAQBAJ|accessdate=19 February 2016|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520105135/https://books.google.ca/books?id=eZyMBQAAQBAJ}}</ref>。

當時加拿大聯邦層面的右翼選票被進步保守黨和加拿大聯盟兩黨攤分，兩者皆難以挑戰[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]的執政地位。彭迪思遂以鼓勵兩黨合併的主張，參與聯邦進步保守黨於2003年5月舉行的黨魁選舉，在第四輪投票以36%對64%得票率敗於[[彼得·麥凱|彼得·-{zh-hans:麦凯;zh-hk:馬逵;zh-tw:麥凱;}-]]<ref name="CBC030601">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-tory-leader-mackay-calls-for-unity-1.358876 |title=New Tory leader MacKay calls for unity |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-06-01 |archive-date=2016-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207104801/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-tory-leader-mackay-calls-for-unity-1.358876 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=2003 PROGRESSIVE CONSERVATIVE LEADERSHIP CONVENTION|url=http://www.cpac.ca/en/2003-progressive-conservative-leadership/|website=cpac.ca|accessdate=19 February 2016|archive-date=2021-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211023223953/https://www.cpac.ca/en/2003-progressive-conservative-leadership/}}</ref>。隨著兩黨於2003年12月合併成新的[[加拿大保守黨|加拿大保守黨]]，彭迪思亦於同月7日宣佈角逐該黨黨魁<ref>{{cite news |url=http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/jim-prentice-timeline-a-long-career-of-public-service |title=Jim Prentice timeline: A long career of public service |publisher=《愛民頓日報》 |accessdate=2016-10-14 |date=2016-10-14 |first=Stuart |last=Thomson |archive-date=2021-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019075812/https://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/jim-prentice-timeline-a-long-career-of-public-service }}</ref>，然而他卻於2004年1月以經費不足為由宣佈棄選<ref>{{cite news |url=http://calgaryherald.com/news/politics/jim-prentice-a-career-that-changed-conservative-politics |title=Jim Prentice: A career that changed Conservative politics |publisher=《卡加利先驅報》 |accessdate=2016-10-14 |date=2016-10-14 |author=Wood, James |coauthor=Varcoe, Chris |archive-date=2016-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017090340/http://calgaryherald.com/news/politics/jim-prentice-a-career-that-changed-conservative-politics |dead-url=no }}</ref>；哈珀最終成為該黨黨魁。

==國會生涯==
彭迪思於[[2004年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2004年加拿大國會下議院選舉]]代表保守黨以54%得票率贏取卡加利北中選區議席<ref>{{cite news|title=244 Calgary North Centre|url=http://www.cbc.ca/canadavotes2004/riding/244/|work=CBC News|accessdate=2016-10-15|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924141021/http://www.cbc.ca/canadavotes2004/riding/244/}}</ref>，首度晉身國會。保守黨在這次選舉成為[[官方反對黨|官方反對黨]]，而彭迪思則獲哈珀委任為該黨的原住民及北方事務評議員，成為[[影子內閣|影子內閣]]一員。彭迪思為黨内對社會議題持相對開放態度的紅色托里派（{{lang|en|Red Tories}}）；他於2005年國會表決《[[民事婚姻法案|民事婚姻法案]]》時投票支持[[加拿大同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ctv.ca/servlet/ArticleNews/scfcn/CTVNews/20050203/same_sex_050203/Canada/ |title=Gay marriage bill reveals party divisions |publisher=Ctv.ca |date=2005-02-03 |accessdate=2010-07-05 |archive-date=2007-11-20 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20071120223819/http://www.ctv.ca/servlet/ArticleNews/scfcn/CTVNews/20050203/same_sex_050203/Canada/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

他於2006年聯邦大選中在更名後的卡加利中北選區連任，而隨着保守黨贏取少數政府，彭迪思亦獲[[加拿大總理|總理]]哈珀邀請[[加拿大內閣|入閣]]，成為聯邦原住民事務及北方發展部長；2007年中則調任工業部長。他在[[2008年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2008年聯邦大選]]中連任卡加利中北選區國會議員，並在保守黨政府中調任環境部長。

2010年11月4日，彭迪思宣佈即時辭任環境部長，並於同年末辭去卡加利中北選區國會議員席位<ref>{{cite news|title=Jim Prentice leave politics for CIBC|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/prentice-quits-cabinet-closes-door-on-political-life/article1216199/|work=《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》|date=2010-11-04|accessdate=2016-10-15|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019075812/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/prentice-quits-cabinet-closes-door-on-political-life/article1216199/}}</ref>；他從2011年起出任[[加拿大帝國商業銀行|加拿大帝國商業銀行]]副主席及高級行政副總裁<ref name="星島160614"/>。

==轉戰省政==
[[File:Prentice_and_Smith.jpg|thumb]]

外界一直盛傳彭迪思有意在哈珀卸任後角逐聯邦保守黨黨魁<ref>{{cite news|title='Draft Jim Prentice' movement urging ex-Harper minister to leave CIBC and run for Alberta PC leadership|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/04/09/draft-jim-prentice-movement-urging-ex-harper-minister-to-leave-cibc-and-run-for-alberta-pc-leadership/|accessdate=2014-05-06|newspaper=National Post|date=2014-04-09}}</ref>，然而他則於2014年宣佈參與亞伯達進步保守黨的黨魁選舉<ref>{{cite news|title=Prentice enters Alberta PC Party Leadership race|url=http://calgary.ctvnews.ca/prentice-enters-alberta-pc-party-leadership-race-1.1823250|accessdate=2014-05-15|newspaper=CTV News|date=2014-05-15|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513032946/https://calgary.ctvnews.ca/prentice-enters-alberta-pc-party-leadership-race-1.1823250|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Jim Prentice forming team for Alberta Tory leadership race|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/jim-prentice-forming-team-for-alberta-tory-leadership-race-1.2624808|accessdate=May 6, 2014|newspaper=CBC News|date=April 28, 2014|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513032951/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/jim-prentice-forming-team-for-alberta-tory-leadership-race-1.2624808|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於同年9月6日舉行的第一輪投票以超過76%得票率當選該黨黨魁<ref>{{cite news|title=Alberta PC leadership vote: Jim Prentice wins on 1st ballot|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/alberta-pc-leadership-vote-jim-prentice-wins-on-1st-ballot-1.2758180?cmp=rss|accessdate=2014-09-06|publisher=CBC News|date=2014-09-06|archive-date=2021-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517112832/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/alberta-pc-leadership-vote-jim-prentice-wins-on-1st-ballot-1.2758180?cmp=rss}}</ref>，同月15日宣誓就任[[亞伯達省省長|亞伯達省省長]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Prentice promises 'new way of doing things' as smaller cabinet sworn in|url=http://www.edmontonjournal.com/Prentice+names+Mandel+health+minister+member+cabinet/10205281/story.html|newspaper=《愛民頓日報》|date=2014-09-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006130519/http://www.edmontonjournal.com/Prentice+names+Mandel+health+minister+member+cabinet/10205281/story.html|archivedate=2014-10-06}}</ref>，再於同年10月27日舉行的[[亞伯達省議會|亞伯達省議會]]議席補選中當選卡加利-山麓選區省議員<ref name=foothills>{{cite news|title=Premier Prentice to run in Calgary-Foothills in October byelection|url=http://globalnews.ca/news/1587770/premier-prentice-to-make-byelection-announcement/|publisher=Global Neww|date=2014-09-29|accessdate=2016-10-19|archive-date=2018-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211090609/https://globalnews.ca/news/1587770/premier-prentice-to-make-byelection-announcement/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

屬中間偏右的亞伯達進步保守黨自1971年起在該省連續執政，但從2000年代末起開始面臨新興右翼政黨野玫瑰黨（{{lang|en|Wildrose Party}}）的威脅。彭迪思就任進步保守黨黨魁後尋求野玫瑰黨省議員的支持，先於2014年11月獲兩名野玫瑰黨省議員轉投進步保守黨<ref name="CP141124">{{cite news|title=Two Wildrose members crossing the floor to join Tories|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/two-wildrose-members-crossing-the-floor-to-join-tories-sources-say/article21733277/|accessdate=2016-10-19|first=Dean|last=Bennett|work=加新社（刊於《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》）|date=2014-11-24|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304111409/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/two-wildrose-members-crossing-the-floor-to-join-tories-sources-say/article21733277/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年12月，野玫瑰黨黨魁戴思敏（{{lang|en|Danielle Smith}}）宣佈她本人與該黨另外八名省議員亦轉投進步保守黨，進步保守黨遂佔省議會87個議席中的70席<ref name="Metro141217">{{cite news|title='I want this premier to succeed' — Wildrose leader Danielle Smith, eight other MLAs join PCs|url=http://www.metronews.ca/news/canada/2014/12/17/nine-wildrose-mlas-bolt-for-alberta-pc-party.html|accessdate=2016-10-19|newspaper=加拿大《[[都市日報|都市日報]]》|date=2014-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827142016/http://www.metronews.ca/news/canada/2014/12/17/nine-wildrose-mlas-bolt-for-alberta-pc-party.html|archive-date=2016-08-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此外，一項於同年12月發表的民意調查顯示彭迪思的支持度達至50%，為全國眾省省長的第二高<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2014-12-17/province1418799632d5367714.html | title=全國省長支持度 彭迪思第二高 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2014-12-17 | accessdate=2016-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020104137/http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2014-12-17/province1418799632d5367714.html | archive-date=2016-10-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

[[File:Jim-Prentice-2015-Provincial-Election-Campaign.jpg|thumb]]

進步保守黨的執政優勢雖獲進一步鞏固，但該黨卻面臨暗湧。國際油價從2014年末起下滑，重創以能源業為重心的亞省經濟，省府庫房收入亦驟減。進步保守黨政府於2015年3月公佈財政預算案，錄得亞省歷來最高的50億元赤字，省府遂增加多項服務收費<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2015-03-28/headline1427523728d5504219.html | title=省服務全面加費 彭迪思籲共度時艱 不敷之數高達70億 | author=郭康立 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2015-03-28 | accessdate=2016-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020103840/http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2015-03-28/headline1427523728d5504219.html | archive-date=2016-10-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。財政預算案公佈前，彭迪思接受[[加拿大廣播公司|加拿大廣播公司]]一個電台節目訪問時表示，省民在瞭解亞省財困的本因時應「反躬自省」（{{lang|en|"look in the mirror"}}），惹來外界批評他將經濟問題歸咎於省民<ref name=electiongaffes>{{cite web|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/mirrors-and-miscalculations-five-alberta-election-moments-to-remember/article24254881/|title=Mirrors and miscalculations: Five Alberta election moments to remember|first=Allan|last=Maki|work=《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》|date=2015-05-05|accessdate=2016-10-19|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308152524/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/mirrors-and-miscalculations-five-alberta-election-moments-to-remember/article24254881/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-03-06/canada1425641209d5468033.html | title=亞省財困諉過省民 反對黨促省長道歉 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2015-03-06 | accessdate=2016-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305003352/http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-03-06/canada1425641209d5468033.html | archive-date=2017-03-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

為了獲取選民授權省府整頓財務，彭迪思於2015年4月7日請示亞省省督解散省議會，並於同年5月5日舉行省選，較原定時間提早一年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/alberta-to-hold-election-on-may-5/article23821249/|title=Jim Prentice seeks mandate on May 5 in cautious Alberta election bid|first=Justin|last=Giovannetti|work=《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》|date=2015-04-07|accessdate=2016-10-19|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019060637/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/alberta/alberta-to-hold-election-on-may-5/article23821249/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-04-08/province1428488107d5521806.html | title=提早1年 亞省突宣布5月5日省選 | author=劉培慶 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2015-04-08 | accessdate=2016-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305004845/http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-04-08/province1428488107d5521806.html | archive-date=2017-03-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。然而，一項民調顯示逾半數受訪者不欲提前舉行省選，並顯示彭迪思的個人支持度跌至29%<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2015-04-02/headline1427956310d5510958.html | title=民調稱逾半省民不欲省選提前 彭迪思民望遜NDP黨魁 | author=郭康立 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2015-04-02 | accessdate=2016-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305003356/http://news.singtao.ca/calgary/2015-04-02/headline1427956310d5510958.html | archive-date=2017-03-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在經濟不景加上選民求變等因素影響下，進步保守黨在該屆省選大敗，只贏取省議會中10個議席，較亞伯達新民主黨和野玫瑰黨皆為少，成為省議會第三大黨。新民主黨首次贏取省議會中多數議席上台執政，進步保守黨在亞省連續執政44年的歲月亦告結束<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-05-06/headline1430907708d5565762.html | title=亞省變天 NDP上台 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2015-05-06 | accessdate=2016-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305004838/http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-05-06/headline1430907708d5565762.html | archive-date=2017-03-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。彭迪思雖保著自己在卡加利-山麓選區的議席，但為了承擔進步保守黨敗選的責任而宣佈即時辭去黨魁和省議員職務<ref>{{cite news|title=Alberta PC Leader Jim Prentice resigns after winning seat in Calgary-Foothills|url=http://globalnews.ca/news/1982058/alberta-pc-leader-jim-prentice-wins-seat-in-calgary-foothills/|accessdate=2015-05-05|work=Global News|date=2015-05-05|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019173551/https://globalnews.ca/news/1982058/alberta-pc-leader-jim-prentice-wins-seat-in-calgary-foothills/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Jim Prentice resigns after orange wave sweeps Alberta|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/elections/alberta-votes/jim-prentice-resigns-after-orange-wave-sweeps-alberta-1.3062789|accessdate=2016-10-19|work=CBC News|date=2015-05-05|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112001310/https://www.cbc.ca/news/elections/alberta-votes/jim-prentice-resigns-after-orange-wave-sweeps-alberta-1.3062789}}</ref>。

==離開政壇、逝世==
彭迪思退出政壇後開始著作一本有關能源和環境議題的書籍，原定於2016年末發行<ref name="CBC161014">{{cite news|title=Jim Prentice's top 5 career highlights|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/jim-prentice-career-highlights-1.3805420|accessdate=2016-10-19|work=CBC News|date=2016-10-14|archive-date=2021-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210723235936/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/calgary/jim-prentice-career-highlights-1.3805420}}</ref>。他亦於2016年6月加入美國華平投資集團（{{lang|en|Warburg Pincus}}），任職能源顧問<ref name="星島160614"/><ref name="CBC161014"/>。

2016年10月13日，彭迪思乘坐一部[[賽斯納|賽斯納]]小型飛機從[[卑詩省|卑詩省]][[基隆拿國際機場|基隆拿國際機場]]飛往[[卡加利|卡加利]]附近的斯普林班克機場（{{lang|en|Springbank Airport}}），飛機起飛不久後在[[湖泊鄉|湖泊鄉]]失事墜毀，他連同機上另外三人罹難<ref name=CBC161013/><ref name="Global161014">{{Cite news | url=http://globalnews.ca/news/3003223/jim-prentice-60-dies-in-kelowna-plane-crash/?sf38890255=1 | title=Jim Prentice, 60, dies in Kelowna plane crash | author=Scotti, Monique | publisher=Global News | date=2016-10-14 | accessdate=2016-10-14 | archive-date=2020-09-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921092505/https://globalnews.ca/news/3003223/jim-prentice-60-dies-in-kelowna-plane-crash/?sf38890255=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。省政府於同月28日在卡加利的南亞伯達金禧大劇院（{{lang|en|Southern Alberta Jubilee Auditorium}}）為他舉行公眾追思會<ref name="Global161028">{{Cite news | url=http://globalnews.ca/news/3026508/jim-prentice-memorial-live-coverage-friday/ | title=Jim Prentice remembered at state memorial: 'he gave Canada and Alberta his very best' | author=Gilligan, Melissa | coauthor=Tucker, Erika | publisher=Global News | date=2016-10-28 | accessdate=2016-11-19 | archive-date=2021-10-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020181326/https://globalnews.ca/news/3026508/jim-prentice-memorial-live-coverage-friday/ }}</ref><ref name="星島161028">{{Cite news | url=http://calgary.singtao.ca/454062/2016-10-28/post-%E5%BD%AD%E8%BF%AA%E6%80%9D%E8%BF%BD%E6%80%9D%E6%9C%83%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C/?variant=zh-hk | title=彭迪思追思會今天舉行 | publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》卡加利版 | date=2016-10-28 | accessdate=2016-11-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161120005954/http://calgary.singtao.ca/454062/2016-10-28/post-%E5%BD%AD%E8%BF%AA%E6%80%9D%E8%BF%BD%E6%80%9D%E6%9C%83%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C/?variant=zh-hk | archive-date=2016-11-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

